These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Color: emerald, aquamarine, amber, lilac
Movie-Genre: disaster, comedy, adventure, spy
1. Color:amber is between Movie-Genre:adventure and Movie-Genre:comedy##2
2. Color:lilac is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:adventure##3
3. Movie-Genre:adventure is not to the left of Movie-Genre:adventure##8
4. Movie-Genre:comedy != Color:amber##6
5. Color:amber is somewhere to the right of Color:emerald##5
6. Color:emerald is on the right of Movie-Genre:disaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | lilac  | emerald | amber | aquamarine  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure   | spy  | comedy |

