.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Hobby: camping, sudoku, video-games, cooking
Game: chess, scrabble, whist, poker
1. Game:poker is not to the left of Game:poker##8
2. Hobby:camping is somewhere to the right of Hobby:cooking##5
3. Hobby:camping == Game:scrabble##1
4. Hobby:cooking is between Hobby:camping and Hobby:sudoku##2
5. Hobby:sudoku is somewhere between Hobby:video-games and Game:chess##7
6. Game:whist is somewhere to the left of Hobby:sudoku##5
7. Game:chess is not to the left of Game:chess##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | sudoku          | cooking | camping     |
| Game    | whist      | poker | chess | scrabble |

