5. Nationality:colombian is on the far left or far right##3
6. Nationality:british is somewhere to the left of Beverage:fanta##5
7. Nationality:colombian == Beverage:juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality           | british | polish | french     | colombian |
